00:21:34.910 --> 00:21:38.290 align:middle line:84%
The alteration of consciousness
in the shamanic ritual

00:21:38.290 --> 00:21:40.450 align:middle line:84%
starts off with a
stimulatory phase--

00:21:40.450 --> 00:21:43.060 align:middle line:84%
dancing, drumming,
singing, chanting--

00:21:43.060 --> 00:21:46.250 align:middle line:84%
to the point of exhaustion
and to the relaxation phase.

00:21:46.250 --> 00:21:48.370 align:middle line:84%
Well, this is a shift
from stimulating

00:21:48.370 --> 00:21:51.240 align:middle line:84%
the sympathetic nervous system
to the parasympathetic nervous

00:21:51.240 --> 00:21:52.040 align:middle line:90%
system.

00:21:52.040 --> 00:21:53.770 align:middle line:84%
The parasympathetic
nervous system

00:21:53.770 --> 00:21:56.500 align:middle line:84%
is the part of the nervous
system that relaxes us.

00:21:56.500 --> 00:21:59.140 align:middle line:84%
And so basically, the
relaxation response

00:21:59.140 --> 00:22:02.830 align:middle line:84%
is part of what's brought
about by ritual activities.

00:22:02.830 --> 00:22:05.960 align:middle line:10%
>> American-based psychoanalyst
Wilhelm Reich mentioned

00:22:05.960 --> 00:22:09.010 align:middle line:10%
a similar pattern when he
spoke about the four stages

00:22:09.010 --> 00:22:12.220 align:middle line:10%
of a primal pattern that
healthy cultures share--

00:22:12.220 --> 00:22:17.070 align:middle line:10%
tension, charge,
discharge, and relaxation.

00:22:17.070 --> 00:22:19.210 align:middle line:84%
It is seen in the
movement of many forms

00:22:19.210 --> 00:22:23.380 align:middle line:84%
of classical and modern music,
all forms of storytelling,

00:22:23.380 --> 00:22:26.380 align:middle line:84%
love-making, as well
as healing catalysts.

00:22:26.380 --> 00:22:28.570 align:middle line:84%
Even though the content
on top of this pattern

00:22:28.570 --> 00:22:31.270 align:middle line:84%
will always change,
the underlying flow

00:22:31.270 --> 00:22:34.480 align:middle line:84%
is what establishes a space
for a healing response.

00:22:34.480 --> 00:22:36.430 align:middle line:84%
Something must dredge
up the traumatized

00:22:36.430 --> 00:22:39.880 align:middle line:84%
psychological material from
the unconscious, which would be

00:22:39.880 --> 00:22:41.830 align:middle line:90%
during the stimulatory phase.

00:22:41.830 --> 00:22:44.920 align:middle line:84%
The contents must be
processed, breathed through,

00:22:44.920 --> 00:22:48.520 align:middle line:84%
and exacerbated in order to
bring about a critical point

00:22:48.520 --> 00:22:52.130 align:middle line:84%
when the psyche transforms
the way it holds that content.

00:22:52.130 --> 00:22:55.150 align:middle line:84%
Finally, the discharge
is a pivot point in which

00:22:55.150 --> 00:22:56.590 align:middle line:90%
breakthroughs are made--

00:22:56.590 --> 00:22:59.710 align:middle line:84%
not by the shaman, but by the
natural healing intelligence

00:22:59.710 --> 00:23:01.900 align:middle line:84%
of the one who is
seeking the remedy.

00:23:01.900 --> 00:23:04.240 align:middle line:84%
This leads to the
relaxation phase,

00:23:04.240 --> 00:23:07.780 align:middle line:84%
which allows a new unhealthy
pattern to integrate.

00:23:07.780 --> 00:23:11.680 align:middle line:84%
This is the same as what's seen
in the Savasana stage of yoga.

00:23:11.680 --> 00:23:14.680 align:middle line:84%
